# ğŸ“Œ 2ï¸âƒ£ Bitwise Operators Theory

| Operator | Meaning     |    |
| -------- | ----------- | -- |
| &        | AND         |    |
|          |             | OR |
| ^        | XOR         |    |
| ~        | NOT         |    |
| <<       | Left Shift  |    |
| >>       | Right Shift |    |

